/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 452.0 Tm ("Hi Jordan, Sam with Northlight again - I tried you earlier in the week, figured the) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 438.0 Tm (timing was just busy. I called because weekend coverage tends to get harder as support) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 424.0 Tm (teams grow, and I help with exactly that. Happy to be quick now if it is a decent) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 410.0 Tm (moment, or I can catch you another time - whichever is easier for you.") Tj
