1 0 0 1 56.0 386.0 Tm (Safe-practice note) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 369.0 Tm (Do not let a second attempt carry any edge of "why did you not call me back" - the) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 355.0 Tm (prospect owes you nothing. Keep attempts spaced and reasonable; repeated rapid calls) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 341.0 Tm (read as pressure. If the second attempt goes nowhere, treat that as a signal, not a) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 327.0 Tm (reason to try five more times.) Tj
